01:11:37.820 --> 01:11:41.640
engineered mouse models, we can see that not only are the

1211
01:11:41.700 --> 01:11:44.980
CD105 positive and CD105 negative fibroblasts

1212
01:11:45.520 --> 01:11:49.220
identifiable across a number of models and also

1213
01:11:49.300 --> 01:11:53.260
in human tissues. But what we can see is that when we

1214
01:11:53.320 --> 01:11:57.100
look more broadly across a number of the sort of very

1215
01:11:57.260 --> 01:12:01.160
